  "content": "<div class=\"css-376mun\"><span id=\"content\"><span class=\"RichText ztext CopyrightRichText-richText css-10o75c2\" options=\"[object Object]\" itemprop=\"text\"><p data-first-child=\"\" data-pid=\"nvNlDuvf\">其实他们两个当初出轨的时候也被骂得狗血淋头的啊，只是中国民众没参与。后来他们(其实只有皮特)还是出了些好作品所以看脸的大家就忘记了……</p><p data-pid=\"RDagvCus\">但是像我这种狭隘的人还是永远讨厌厚嘴唇小三！<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=8147913&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=2&amp;q=%E7%9A%AE%E7%89%B9&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">皮特<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>和安尼斯顿当年才真真是金童玉女，两人一起出现的时候都有小花朵在飘落，有满天繁星在blingbling闪烁~</p><p data-pid=\"Nw_Qsni2\">真爱真的不一定白头到老的</p></span><span id=\"VirtualCatalogAnchorPoint\"></span></span></div>",
